有约 7300 万活跃用户，而 X 的活跃用户为 3.65 亿。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>向欧盟扩张无疑将增强 Thread 的全球参与度，但时间会证明其速度和程度。去年 10 月，Meta 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格 (Mark Zuckerberg) 预测，Threads 在未来几年内可能会覆盖 10 亿用户。人们可以使用 Instagram 快速创建 Threads 帐户，它拥有超过 20 亿活跃用户，但直到推出八年后才突破<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-06-20-instagram-1-billion-users.html">10 亿大关</a>。 Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri 还宣布，删除您的 Threads 帐户<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-will-allow-users-to-delete-accounts-separately-from-instagram-160038998.html">将不再删除您关联的 Instagram 帐户</a>——这是另一个争论点。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/threads-may-finally-launch-in-europe-in​​-december-124054154.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/threads-may-finally-launch-in-europe-in-december-124054154.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0eb811db-10e3-4dc4-95de-9b58d095ef9d</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:40:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701347641</ingested><modified> 2023-11-30T12:34:04+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="1780" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Faaffdce0-827a-11ee-9e71-5c953615e289&amp;resize=3000%2C1780&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b91eae5a3e88175d86e162994ee55b9769e608c8" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:desc