候马斯克发推文后决定<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-reportedly-pulls-ads-from-x-amid-a-growing-backlash-to-antisemitic-content-on-the-platform-205849759.html">撤回广告的</a>决定。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/bob-iger-criticizes-chapek-disappointed-in-what-i-was-seeing-1235813338/">据</a><em>Variety</em>报道，艾格表示迪士尼与 X 的合作“对我们来说不一定是积极的”。</p><p>虽然马斯克再次否认自己是反犹太主义者，但他确实对参与导致广告商再次离开 X 的推文表示了一些遗憾。 ”马斯克在谈到这篇<em>文章</em><a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://variety.com/2023/digital/news/elon-musk-x-twitter-advertisers-antisemitic-post-spending-go-f-yourself-1235813657/">时</a>说道。</p><p> X 没有立即回应置评请求。据<em>《好莱坞报道》报道，</em> X 首席执行官琳达·亚卡里诺 (Linda Yaccarino) 坐在前排观看了这番言论，该报<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/elon-musk-talks-x-advertiser-exodus-dealbook-summit-1235698937/">报道称</a>，在马斯克的长篇大论中，这位前广告高管“面无表情”地坐着。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-responds-companies-pulled-233913536.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-responds-companies-pulled-233913536.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb9d42a8-7c8b-4cca-9d62-1d9c6c636cb5</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 23:39:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701304462</ingested><modified> 2023-11-30T00:34:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="2045" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2F5f680cc0-8f0f-11ee-beff-a3c1724973e6&amp;resize=3000%2C2045&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b1794fc310ca35cb15ded9ef758d759c3cd168d8" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2045" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2F5f680cc0-8f0f-11ee-beff-a3c1724973e6&amp;resize=3000%2C2045&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=6c0f6ada92ec6d2f9ecb38ff851a433d88a4912f" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Slaven Vlasic via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[NEW YORK, NEW YORK - NOVEMBER 29: Elon Musk speaks onstage during The New York Times Dealbook Summit 2023 at Jazz at Lincoln Center on November 29, 2023 in New York City. (Photo by Slaven Vlasic/Getty Images for The New York Times)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The New York Times Dealbook Summit 2023]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[EVs are way more unreliable than gas-powered cars, Consumer Reports data indicates]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <em>《消费者报告》</em> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.consumerreports.org/cars/car-reliability-owner-satisfaction/who-makes-the-most-reliable-cars-a7824554938/" data-original-link="https://www.consumerreports.org/cars/car-reliability-owner-satisfaction/who-makes-the-most-reliable-cars-a7824554938/">发布了</a>广泛的汽车可靠性排名，结果给<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/evs/">电动汽车</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lamborghinis-plug-in-hybrid-supercar-runs-for-a-cool-six-miles-in-electric-only-mode-183728414.html">插电式混合动力</a>汽车的可靠性泼了一盆冷水。调查显示，电动汽车的维护问题比汽油或柴油汽车多 79%，而插电式混合动力汽车的问题多 146%。这些麻烦描绘了随着地球<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/july-3rd-was-the-hottest-day-in-recorded-history-214854746.html">气温创下历史新高</a>，该行业在相对较新的技术方面面临的成长烦恼，科学家<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/we-have-three-years-to-curb-emissions-to-avoid-climate-catastrophe-un-report-finds-204058474.html">警告称，阻止全球气候灾难的最后期限很快就会到来</a>。</p><p>该调查对<em>CR</em>会员过去一年的乘车问题进行了调查，收集了 330,000 辆车的数据。该出版物的数据包括 2000 年至 2023 年的车型，以及一些（早期推出的）2024 年车型。 <em>CR</em>研究了 20 个“问题区域”，包括刹车吱吱作响或内饰损坏等相对较小的问题，以及与变速箱、发动机或电动汽车电池相关的问题较多的问题。潜在故障区域的数量因类型而异：内燃机 (ICE) 车辆有 17 个，电动汽车有 12 个，传统混合动力汽车有 19 个，插电式混合动力汽车有全部 20 个。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该出版物将这些数据与自己的赛道测试、车主满意度调查结果和安全信息结合起来。然后对其进行平均，为每个品牌分配一个数字分数（满分 100 分）。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/7d96b120-8efa-11ee-9d75-afc08ef63c94" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/7d96b120-8efa-11ee-9d75-afc08ef63c94" style="height:747px;width:1244px;" alt="雷克萨斯 UX 混合动力汽车的营销照片。银色车型在灯光璀璨的城市街道上行驶。" data-uuid="fae52d51-e390-3e52-afa8-d37cc5806428"><figcaption>雷克萨斯 UX 是一款罕见的插电式混合动力车，在调查中得分很高。</figcaption><div class="photo-credit">雷克萨斯</div></figure><p>非插电式混合动力汽车得分很高，调查显示，它们遇到的问题比汽油和柴油动力汽车少 26%。 <em>CR</em>重点介绍了该领域最可靠的品牌，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-03-27-lexus-offers-subscription-service.html">雷克萨斯的 UX</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-lexus-nx-300-nx-200900545.html">NX 混合动力车</a>以及<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-toyota-camry-gets-updates-110000522.html">丰田的凯美瑞混合动力车</a>、汉兰达混合动力车和 RAV4 混合动力车。</p><p>如果插电式混合动力车（PHEV）能够享受这些评级就好了。相反，与传统汽油动力汽车相比，它们的故障点清单更长，导致的问题多出 146%。表现不佳的包括<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/chrysler-pacifica-hybrid-2018-phev-recall-irl-131527040.html">克莱斯勒 Pacifica</a> （满分 100 分，得分为 14 分）和<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-audi-q5-first-drive-150000639.html">奥迪 Q5</a> 。然而，一些插电式混合动力汽车超出了该类别的预期，其中包括<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/toyota-rav-4-prime-priced-at-40000-195446077.html">丰田 RAV4 Prime</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/kia-sportage-phev-suv-america-175104167.html">起亚 Sportage</a>等“佼佼者”。其他几款车型，包括<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-09-27-2019-bmw-x5-review.html">宝马 X5</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/next-gen-hyundai-tucson-reveals-143200862.html">现代途胜</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-ford-escape-hybrid-fuel-212000954.html">福特 Escape</a> ，在可靠性方面得分为“平均”。</p><p>许多汽车制造商计划<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lincoln-all-electric-vehicles-2030-100028732.html">在 2030 年之前将其经销店装满的</a>全电动汽车和 SUV 的平均得分一般：分别为 44 分和 43 分。 <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rivians-electric-truck-is-available-to-lease-in-14-us-states-215636074.html">电动皮卡</a>是这一系列中的最新技术，其得分较低，平均分为 30 分，这也许并不令人意外。</p><p>雷克萨斯在电动汽车品牌中名列前茅。除一款外，其所有型号在<em>CR</em>的评级中均得分高于平均水平或更高。唯一的例外是 NX，得分仍然处于平均水平。丰田也表现出色，其中包括<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-toyota-4runner-review-living-150000641.html">4Runner SUV</a> ，CR 称其为“调查中最可靠的车型之一”。然而，其电动<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-toyota-land-cruiser-4runner-110000083.html">坦途皮卡</a>得分不佳。其他得分高于平均水平的电动汽车包括 <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-02-27-2019-acura-rdx-review.html">讴歌的 RDX</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2021-acura-tlx-vs-luxury-170100103.html">TLX</a> 。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/d6d86c60-8efa-11ee-93ef-0833cf2851bf" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/d6d86c60-8efa-11ee-93ef-0833cf2851bf" style="height:800px;width:1334px;" alt="特斯拉 Model 3 停在户外田野旁的照片。远处可见绿草、树木和山丘。" data-uuid="4f9247d3-e1c5-38e4-a436-4226848c4583"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">罗伯托·鲍德温 / Engadget 摄</div></figure><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-03-01-tesla-model-3-review.html">特斯拉</a>曾经几乎是电动汽车的代名词，但其总体得分处于中等水平（与雪佛兰、别克、拉姆、凯迪拉克和道奇等品牌并列）。 <em>CR</em>表示，埃隆·马斯克领导的公司的电动汽车动力系统往往比传统汽车制造商的动力系统表现更好。然而， <em>Ars Technica</em> <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:23;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://arstechnica.com/cars/2023/11/evs-have-79-more-reliability-problems-than-gas-cars-says-consumer-reports/" data-original-link="https://arstechnica.com/cars/2023/11/evs-have-79-more-reliability-problems-than-gas-cars-says-consumer-reports/">指出</a>，该公司的可靠性得分在车身、油漆/装饰和气候系统等方面表现不佳。</p><p>从地区来看，亚洲汽车制造商在调查中的平均得分最高，为 63 分。欧洲公司排名第二，平均得分为 46 分，而美国品牌则下滑，得分为 39 分，有些令人失望。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/evs-are-way-more-unreliable-than-gas-powered-cars-consumer-reports-data-indicates-212216581.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/evs-are-way-more-unreliable-than-gas-powered-cars-consumer-reports-data-indicates-212216581.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 51218DFB-45F4-4C37-8650-686043CBEC0E</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 21:22:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701294327</ingested><modified> 2023-11-29T21:45:36+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nature & Environment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1833" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Fc01cae10-8ef9-11ee-9d77-64bb3de436c7&amp;resize=3000%2C1833&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=8b6e87293ac8ee61c178e4d9d3af649d68b10b42" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1833" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Fc01cae10-8ef9-11ee-9d77-64bb3de436c7&amp;resize=3000%2C1833&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=cf184f3dd2c2f8f79c67b3628cea1ab99d4869f6" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Photo by Roberto Baldwin / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Photo of the Rivian R1S electric SUV (red) sitting by a beach with rocky shores.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Rivian R1S]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Rockstar Games co-founder Dan Houser's next projects are a graphic novel and an audio drama]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Rockstar Games 联合创始人兼前创意总监 Dan Houser 成立的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-games-co-founder-dan-houser-has-a-new-studio-183054769.html">新创意工作室</a>Absurd Ventures<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.absurdventures.com/feed">宣布了其第一个项目</a>。碰巧的是，它们都不是电子游戏，至少现在还不是。</p><p>这两个新宇宙中的第一个名为<em>“American Caper”</em> ，它将作为图画小说首次亮相。它将聚焦于两个正常但受损的家庭，他们深陷“腐败的商业、无能的政治和笨拙的犯罪的世界”。漫画艺术家西蒙·比斯利（ <em>ABC Warriors、Lobo</em> ）正在为这本图画小说绘制插图。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>另一个项目是一部已经在制作中的 12 集音频剧。 <em>《美好天堂》</em>被描述为一部近未来存在悬疑惊悚片。 Absurd Ventures 正在与知名音频公司 Q-CODE Media 合作开展该项目。</p><p> Absurd Ventures 计划在未来几个月内透露有关这两个项目的更多细节。然而，将《American Caper》和《A Better Paradise》都称为“宇宙”表明该公司计划将其扩展到跨媒体企业，其中可能只包括视频游戏。</p><p>与此同时，距离我们第一次真正了解过去几年 Houser 在 Rockstar 的前同事们忙碌的原因只有几天了。发行商将于 12 月初<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-first-grand-theft-auto-vi-trailer-will-arrive-in-early-december-045219564.html">发布下一款侠盗猎车手游戏的首个预告片</a>。有传言称该揭晓将于 12 月 7 日的游戏颁奖典礼上揭晓。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-games-co-Founder-dan-housers-next-projects-are-a-graphic-novel-and-an-audio-drama-210258054 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-games-co-founder-dan-housers-next-projects-are-a-graphic-novel-and-an-audio-drama-210258054.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> efea7705-b77d-4b9a-8d38-854c72ca5012</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 21:02:58 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701291779</ingested><modified> 2023-11-29T21:03:02+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1689" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2F5b122220-8ef9-11ee-bfdf-8a7c672d9ae2&amp;resize=3000%2C1689&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=092c5c131bedaabb2ec6ea7297690a6a4029201b" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1689" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2F5b122220-8ef9-11ee-bfdf-8a7c672d9ae2&amp;resize=3000%2C1689&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=e5bcb02aed063ddd2d734d86c6b5d8f7ff3506ba" width="3000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Absurd Ventures]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Absurd Ventures logos for A Better Paradise and American Caper.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Absurd Ventures logos for A Better Paradise and American Caper.]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>